<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-16 13:23 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1267 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LYNCH-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      06-16 0658
