   COX-CABLE _ Cox Communications has bought a cable TV system in
Tucson, Ariz., its second major purchase in the past two months.
The Atlanta-based company is buying the system, which has 119,000
subscribers in Tucson and other surrounding Arizona towns, from
Tele-Communications Inc. Terms of the deal were not disclosed.
(Haddad, Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
