promised to be as dominant as Coke or Nike. It boasted as it won
media attention across the country. A year and a half since the
debut of Monorail the computer and Monorail the company, the
executives of the Marietta-based firm have kept up the marketing
chutzpah, but the market hasn't bought in as planned. (Kempner,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
