   10. Singin' in the Rain (1952)
</P>
<P>
   11. It's a Wonderful Life (1946)
</P>
<P>
   12. Sunset Boulevard (1950)
</P>
<P>
   13. The Bridge on the River Kwai (1957)
</P>
<P>
   14. Some Like It Hot (1959)
</P>
<P>
   15. Star Wars (1977)
</P>
<P>
   16. All About Eve (1950)
</P>
<P>
   17. The African Queen (1951)
</P>
<P>
   18. Psycho (1960)
