</P>
<P>
   MY DARLING CLEMENTINE
</P>
<P>
   MY FAIR LADY
</P>
<P>
   MY MAN GODFREY
</P>
<P>
   NASHVILLE
</P>
<P>
   NATIONAL LAMPOON'S ANIMAL HOUSE
</P>
<P>
   NETWORK
</P>
<P>
   A NIGHT AT THE OPERA
</P>
<P>
   THE NIGHT OF THE HUNTER
</P>
<P>
   NIGHT OF THE LIVING DEAD
</P>
<P>
