QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-ELDERLY-PAIN-STUDY-NYT, which
moved in ``a'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``At some point, nursing home staff and in-house doctors may
give up on patients who they know are going to die. There is no
acceptable excuse for not treating pain appropriately in terminally
ill patients.''
</P>
<P>
   _DR. GIOVANNI GAMBASSI, a co-author of a study on the
undermedication of elderly cancer patients.
