<HEADER>
A2361 &Cx1f; tic-z
u v &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-AZR-BUDGET-AZR &LR;      06-16 0034
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-AZR-BUDGET-AZR </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
BC- ELIMINATE_ELIMINATE-AZR
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
